      "text": "あ、ありがとうございます……じゃなくて\n莉央さん、どうしてここに？　しかもこんな時間に……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ thank you… no‚ wait—\nRio-san‚ why are you here? And at this hour…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 244.1999992371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
