      "text": "……今晩は落ち着かなくて、走りに来ちゃったの\n貴方こそ、こんな場所で何ボーっと突っ立ってるのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…But tonight I couldn’t relax‚ so I came to run.\nAnd you‚ what are you doing just standing here spacing out?",
        "id": ""
